Using the above syntax, you can add to the array using the following
code:

   push (@{$commands{$mostrecenttarget}}, $LINE);

For a full discussion you can check out the "Making Hashes of Arrays"
recipe from the "Perl Cookbook" via the previously mentioned Safari
Books Online.

